// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
// MENU SYSTEM â€” Hierarchical Navigation Configuration
// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

model MenuGroup {
  id        String     @id @default(uuid())
  code      String     @unique
  label     String
  icon      String     @default("FileText")
  sortOrder Int        @default(0)
  isActive  Boolean    @default(true)
  items     MenuItem[]
  roleAccess RoleAccess[]

  @@index([code])
  @@index([sortOrder])
}

model MenuItem {
  id        String    @id @default(uuid())
  groupId   String
  label     String
  page      String    @default("")
  icon      String    @default("FileText")
  sortOrder Int       @default(0)
  isActive  Boolean   @default(true)
  isHidden  Boolean   @default(false)
  parentId  String?
  group     MenuGroup @relation(fields: [groupId], references: [id])
  parent    MenuItem? @relation("MenuItemChildren", fields: [parentId], references: [id])
  children  MenuItem[] @relation("MenuItemChildren")

  @@index([groupId])
  @@index([parentId])
  @@index([page])
  @@index([sortOrder])
}

model RoleAccess {
  id      String    @id @default(uuid())
  groupId String
  roleId  String
  canView Boolean   @default(true)
  group   MenuGroup @relation(fields: [groupId], references: [id])

  @@unique([groupId, roleId])
  @@index([roleId])
  @@index([groupId])
}

// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
// MAINTENANCE MODULE
// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

model MaintenanceTicket {
  id                      String    @id @default(uuid())
  ticketNo                String    @unique
  type                    String    @default("complaint")     // complaint, work_request, emergency, inspection, quotation, preventive_maintenance
  category                String    @default("general_maintenance")  // air_conditioning, electrical, plumbing, fire_protection, mechanical, civil, cleaning, security, it, general_maintenance, other
  priority                String    @default("medium")       // emergency, high, medium, low, preventive
  subject                 String
  description             String @db.Text
  status                  String    @default("new")          // new, under_review, assigned, accepted, in_progress, pending_parts, pending_customer, completed, customer_verification, closed
  source                  String    @default("manual")       // manual, whatsapp, email, portal, phone
  customerId              String?
  siteId                  String?
  building                String?
  floor                   String?
  room                    String?
  equipmentId             String?
  projectId               String?
  contactPerson           String?
  contactPhone            String?
  location                String?
  preferredVisitDate      DateTime?
  preferredVisitTime      String?
  photos                  String?                              // JSON array
  videos                  String?                              // JSON array
  documents               String?                              // JSON array
  assignedTechnicianId    String?
  assignedAt              DateTime?
  acceptedAt              DateTime?
  startedAt               DateTime?
  completedAt             DateTime?
  closedAt                DateTime?
  responseDeadline        DateTime?
  resolutionDeadline      DateTime?
  slaBreached             Boolean   @default(false)
  actualResponseMinutes  Float?                               // minutes from creation to first response
  actualResolutionMinutes Float?                              // minutes from creation to resolution/close
  labourHours             Float     @default(0)
  materialCost            Float     @default(0)
  serviceCost             Float     @default(0)
  transportCost           Float     @default(0)
  totalCost               Float     @default(0)
  closedById              String?
  assignedTeamId          String?
  customerApproved        Boolean   @default(false)
  customerApprovedAt      DateTime?
  customerRating          Int?
  customerFeedback        String?   @db.Text
  customerSignature       String?   @db.Text
  cancelledReason         String? @db.Text
  whatsappConversationId  String?  @unique
  whatsappContactId       String?  @unique
  createdById             String
  createdAt               DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt               DateTime @updatedAt
  customer                Customer? @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  site                    MaintenanceSite? @relation(fields: [siteId], references: [id])
  equipment               Asset? @relation(fields: [equipmentId], references: [id])
  project                 Project? @relation(fields: [projectId], references: [id])
  assignedTechnician      TechnicianProfile?  @relation(fields: [assignedTechnicianId], references: [id])
  createdBy               User                @relation("MaintenanceTickets", fields: [createdById], references: [id])
  closedBy                User?               @relation("MaintenanceTicketsClosedBy", fields: [closedById], references: [id])
  timeline                MaintenanceTimeline[]
  workOrders              MaintenanceWorkOrder[]
  invoices                MaintenanceInvoice[]
  materialRequests        MaterialRequest[]
  whatsappConversation    WhatsAppConversation? @relation("TicketConversation", fields: [whatsappConversationId], references: [id])
  whatsappContact         WhatsAppContact?    @relation("TicketContact", fields: [whatsappContactId], references: [id])

  @@index([ticketNo])
  @@index([status])
  @@index([priority])
  @@index([category])
  @@index([type])
  @@index([source])
  @@index([customerId])
  @@index([siteId])
  @@index([assignedTechnicianId])
  @@index([createdById])
  @@index([createdAt])
  @@index([whatsappConversationId])
  @@index([whatsappContactId])
}

model MaintenanceTimeline {
  id             String   @id @default(uuid())
  ticketId       String
  action         String                                       // new, under_review, assigned, accepted, in_progress, pending_parts, pending_customer, completed, customer_verification, closed, comment, status_change, escalation, sla_breach
  description    String @db.Text
  performedById  String?
  metadata       String?                                       // JSON for extra context
  createdAt      DateTime @default(now())

  ticket         MaintenanceTicket @relation(fields: [ticketId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  performedBy    User?             @relation("MaintenanceTimelineUser", fields: [performedById], references: [id])

  @@index([ticketId])
  @@index([createdAt])
}

model TechnicianProfile {
  id                  String    @id @default(uuid())
  userId              String    @unique
  employeeId          String?
  specialties         String?                                 // JSON array of category strings
  availabilityStatus  String    @default("available")        // available, busy, offline, on_leave
  rating              Float     @default(0)
  totalJobsCompleted  Int       @default(0)
  totalJobsActive     Int       @default(0)
  totalCompletedJobs  Int       @default(0)
  totalActiveJobs     Int       @default(0)
  specializations     String?                                 // JSON array of category strings (alias of specialties)
  certifications      String?                                 // JSON array of certifications
  latitude            Float?
  longitude           Float?
  currentLocation     String?                                 // JSON { lat, lng, address }
  maxJobsPerDay       Int       @default(5)
  phone               String?
  emergencyContact    String?
  bio                 String? @db.Text
  createdAt           DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt           DateTime @updatedAt
  user                User                   @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  employee            Employee?              @relation(fields: [employeeId], references: [id])
  tickets             MaintenanceTicket[]
  workOrders          MaintenanceWorkOrder[]
  serviceRatings      ServiceRating[]
  pmSchedules         PMSchedule[]

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([availabilityStatus])
  @@index([rating])
}

model MaintenanceWorkOrder {
  id                    String    @id @default(uuid())
  workOrderNo           String    @unique
  ticketId              String    @unique
  customerId            String?
  assignedTechnicianId  String?
  assignedTeamId        String?
  startDate             DateTime?
  targetCompletionDate  DateTime?
  actualStartDate       DateTime?
  actualCompletionDate  DateTime?
  status                String    @default("pending")         // pending, in_progress, paused, completed, cancelled
  serviceNotes          String? @db.Text
  completionNotes       String? @db.Text
  labourHours           Float?
  costEstimate          Float?
  actualCost            Float?
  materialCost          Float     @default(0)
  serviceCost           Float     @default(0)
  totalCost             Float     @default(0)
  photos                String?                                 // JSON array of photo URLs
  customerSignature     String?                                 // base64 signature
  createdById           String
  createdAt             DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt             DateTime @updatedAt
  ticket                MaintenanceTicket  @relation(fields: [ticketId], references: [id])
  customer              Customer? @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  assignedTechnician    TechnicianProfile? @relation(fields: [assignedTechnicianId], references: [id])
  createdBy             User                @relation("WorkOrdersCreatedBy", fields: [createdById], references: [id])
  materialRequests      MaterialRequest[]
  invoice               MaintenanceInvoice?

  @@index([workOrderNo])
  @@index([ticketId])
  @@index([status])
  @@index([assignedTechnicianId])
  @@index([customerId])
  @@index([createdById])
}

model MaintenanceSite {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  name        String
  code        String   @unique
  customerId  String?
  description String? @db.Text
  address     String? @db.Text
  district    String?
  phone       String?
  email       String?
  contactPerson String?
  contactPhone String?
  managerName String?
  managerPhone String?
  latitude    Float?
  longitude   Float?
  isActive    Boolean  @default(true)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  customer    Customer? @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  tickets     MaintenanceTicket[]
  pmSchedules PMSchedule[]

  @@index([code])
  @@index([isActive])
  @@index([customerId])
}

model SLATemplate {
  id                    String   @id @default(uuid())
  priority              String   @unique                        // emergency, high, medium, low
  name                  String?
  description           String?  @db.Text
  label                 String?
  responseTimeMinutes   Int      @default(240)                  // minutes to first response
  resolutionTimeMinutes Int      @default(1440)                 // minutes to resolution
  escalationAfterMinutes Int    @default(120)                  // minutes before escalation
  isActive              Boolean  @default(true)
  createdAt             DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt             DateTime @updatedAt

  @@index([priority])
}

model MaterialRequest {
  id              String    @id @default(uuid())
  requestNo       String    @unique
  ticketId        String?
  workOrderId     String?
  siteId          String?
  requestedById   String
  items           String                                  // JSON array of {name, quantity, unit, specification}
  status          String    @default("pending")          // pending, approved, ordered, delivered, cancelled
  urgencyLevel    String    @default("normal")            // normal, urgent, emergency
  notes           String? @db.Text
  totalCost       Float?
  approvedById    String?
  approvedAt      DateTime?
  supervisorApprovedById String?
  supervisorApprovedAt   DateTime?
  issuedById      String?
  createdAt       DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime @updatedAt
  ticket          MaintenanceTicket?   @relation(fields: [ticketId], references: [id])
  workOrder       MaintenanceWorkOrder? @relation(fields: [workOrderId], references: [id])
  requestedBy     User                 @relation("MaterialRequests", fields: [requestedById], references: [id])
  approvedBy      User?                @relation("MaterialApprovedBy", fields: [approvedById], references: [id])
  supervisorApprovedBy User?           @relation("MaterialSupervisorApproved", fields: [supervisorApprovedById], references: [id])
  issuedBy        User?                @relation("MaterialIssuedBy", fields: [issuedById], references: [id])

  @@index([requestNo])
  @@index([ticketId])
  @@index([workOrderId])
  @@index([status])
  @@index([requestedById])
}

model AMCContract {
  id              String    @id @default(uuid())
  contractNo      String    @unique
  name            String?
  description     String?   @db.Text
  customerId      String
  siteId          String?
  createdById     String?
  startDate       DateTime
  endDate         DateTime
  status          String    @default("active")              // active, expired, cancelled
  contractValue   Float     @default(0)
  annualValue     Float?
  coveredEquipment String? @db.Text
  slaPriority     String?
  renewalDate     DateTime?
  autoRenew       Boolean   @default(false)
  customer        Customer  @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  createdBy       User?     @relation("AMCCreatedBy", fields: [createdById], references: [id])
  coveredServices String?                                  // JSON array of service categories
  visitFrequency  String    @default("monthly")             // weekly, biweekly, monthly, quarterly
  totalVisits     Int       @default(12)
  usedVisits      Int       @default(0)
  responseSla     String    @default("medium")              // emergency, high, medium, low
  priorityLevel   String    @default("high")               // emergency, high, medium, low
  notes           String? @db.Text
  createdAt       DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime  @updatedAt

  @@index([contractNo])
  @@index([customerId])
  @@index([status])
  @@index([startDate])
  @@index([endDate])
}

// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
// WHATSAPP EXTENDED MODELS
// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

model WhatsAppBotLog {
  id              String    @id @default(uuid())
  sessionId       String
  conversationId  String?
  contactId       String?
  command         String                                     // STATUS, MY_REQUESTS, HELP, etc.
  inputMessage    String? @db.Text
  responseMessage String? @db.Text
  processingTimeMs Int?
  createdAt       DateTime  @default(now())

  @@index([sessionId])
  @@index([conversationId])
  @@index([contactId])
  @@index([command])
  @@index([createdAt])
}

model WhatsAppDepartment {
  id          String    @id @default(uuid())
  name        String
  accountId   String
  department  String                                    // maintenance, projects, sales, support
  isActive    Boolean   @default(true)
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())

  account     WhatsAppAccount @relation(fields: [accountId], references: [id])

  @@index([department])
  @@index([isActive])
}

// ============ QR CODE MANAGEMENT SYSTEM ============

model QRCode {
  id            String   @id @default(uuid())
  qrId          String   @unique
  moduleType    String
  recordId      String
  referenceNo   String?
  title         String?
  token         String
  securityHash  String
  metadata      String?  @db.Text
  isActive      Boolean  @default(true)
  expiresAt     DateTime?
  generatedById String
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt     DateTime @updatedAt
  generatedBy   User             @relation(fields: [generatedById], references: [id])
  scanLogs      QRScanLog[]
  verifications QRVerification[]

  @@index([moduleType])
  @@index([recordId])
  @@index([moduleType, recordId])
  @@index([token])
  @@index([qrId])
  @@index([generatedById])
}

model QRScanLog {
  id          String    @id @default(uuid())
  qrCodeId    String
  scannedById String?
  scanType    String    @default("scan")
  deviceInfo  String?   @db.Text
  ipAddress   String?
  userAgent   String?
  location    String?   @db.Text
  latitude    Float?
  longitude   Float?
  verified    Boolean   @default(false)
  result      String?   @db.Text
  scannedAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  qrCode      QRCode    @relation(fields: [qrCodeId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  scannedBy   User?     @relation(fields: [scannedById], references: [id])

  @@index([qrCodeId])
  @@index([scannedById])
  @@index([scannedAt])
  @@index([verified])
}

model QRVerification {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  qrCodeId    String
  attemptedAt DateTime @default(now())
  ipAddress   String?
  userAgent   String?
  success     Boolean
  failReason  String?
  moduleType  String?
  recordId    String?
  qrCode      QRCode   @relation(fields: [qrCodeId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([qrCodeId])
  @@index([ipAddress])
  @@index([attemptedAt])
  @@index([success])
}

model QRPrintJob {
  id          String    @id @default(uuid())
  jobName     String
  moduleType  String
  template    String    @default("standard")
  qrCodeIds   String    @db.Text
  totalItems  Int
  status      String    @default("pending")
  createdById String
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  completedAt DateTime?
  createdBy   User      @relation(fields: [createdById], references: [id])

  @@index([createdById])
  @@index([status])
  @@index([createdAt])
}

model QRAuditLog {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  action      String
  qrId        String?
  moduleType  String?
  recordId    String?
  performedBy String?
  ipAddress   String?
  userAgent   String?
  details     String?  @db.Text
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())

  @@index([action])
  @@index([moduleType])
  @@index([performedBy])
  @@index([createdAt])
}

model QRTemplate {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  name        String
  moduleType  String
  template    String   @db.Text
  isDefault   Boolean  @default(false)
  createdById String
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt
  createdBy   User     @relation(fields: [createdById], references: [id])

  @@index([moduleType])
  @@index([isDefault])
}

// ── Enterprise Job Queue ─────────────────────────────────────────────
model JobQueue {
  id          String    @id @default(uuid())
  type        String
  payload     String    @db.Text
  status      String    @default("pending")
  attempts    Int       @default(0)
  maxAttempts Int       @default(3)
  error       String?   @db.Text
  nextRunAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  lockedAt    DateTime?
  lockedBy    String?
  completedAt DateTime?
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime  @updatedAt

  @@index([status, nextRunAt])
  @@index([type])
  @@index([createdAt])
}

// ── Guaranteed Complaint Inbox (zero-loss buffer) ────────────────────
model ComplaintInbox {
  id          String    @id @default(uuid())
  source      String
  rawData     String    @db.Text
  status      String    @default("pending")
  attempts    Int       @default(0)
  processedAt DateTime?
  error       String?   @db.Text
  complaintId String?
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())

  @@index([status])
  @@index([source])
  @@index([createdAt])
}

// ── System Event Log ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
model SystemEvent {
  id         String   @id @default(uuid())
  eventType  String
  entityType String?
  entityId   String?
  userId     String?
  payload    String?  @db.Text
  createdAt  DateTime @default(now())

  @@index([eventType])
  @@index([entityType, entityId])
  @@index([userId])
  @@index([createdAt])
}

// ── Maintenance Invoice (generated on work-order completion) ──────────
model MaintenanceInvoice {
  id             String    @id @default(uuid())
  invoiceNo      String    @unique
  ticketId       String?
  workOrderId    String?   @unique
  customerId     String
  labourCost     Float     @default(0)
  materialCost   Float     @default(0)
  transportCost  Float     @default(0)
  serviceCharges Float     @default(0)
  tax            Float     @default(0)
  discount       Float     @default(0)
  total          Float     @default(0)
  paidAmount     Float     @default(0)
  status         String    @default("draft")   // draft, sent, paid, partial, cancelled
  notes          String?   @db.Text
  issuedById     String
  createdAt      DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt      DateTime  @updatedAt

  ticket         MaintenanceTicket?    @relation(fields: [ticketId], references: [id])
  workOrder      MaintenanceWorkOrder? @relation(fields: [workOrderId], references: [id])
  customer       Customer              @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  issuedBy       User                  @relation("MaintenanceInvoiceIssuedBy", fields: [issuedById], references: [id])

  @@index([invoiceNo])
  @@index([ticketId])
  @@index([workOrderId])
  @@index([customerId])
  @@index([status])
}

// ── Preventive Maintenance Schedule ──────────────────────────────────
model PMSchedule {
  id                    String    @id @default(uuid())
  scheduleNo            String    @unique
  customerId            String?
  siteId                String?
  equipmentId           String?
  assetId               String?
  scheduleType          String                       // monthly, quarterly, semi_annual, annual
  frequencyMonths       Int       @default(1)
  assignedTechnicianId  String?
  description           String?   @db.Text
  lastVisitDate         DateTime?
  nextVisitDate         DateTime?
  totalVisits           Int       @default(12)
  completedVisits       Int       @default(0)
  autoGenerateWorkOrder Boolean   @default(true)
  isActive              Boolean   @default(true)
  createdById           String
  createdAt             DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt             DateTime  @updatedAt

  customer              Customer?          @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  site                  MaintenanceSite?   @relation(fields: [siteId], references: [id])
  assignedTechnician    TechnicianProfile? @relation(fields: [assignedTechnicianId], references: [id])
  createdBy             User               @relation("PMScheduleCreatedBy", fields: [createdById], references: [id])

  @@index([scheduleNo])
  @@index([customerId])
  @@index([siteId])
  @@index([assignedTechnicianId])
  @@index([nextVisitDate])
  @@index([isActive])
}

// ── Service Rating (customer feedback on completed jobs) ──────────────
model ServiceRating {
  id                   String    @id @default(uuid())
  ticketId             String?
  workOrderId          String?
  technicianProfileId  String?
  customerId           String?
  rating               Int       @default(0)        // 1-5
  category             String?
  comment              String?   @db.Text
  createdAt            DateTime  @default(now())

  technicianProfile    TechnicianProfile? @relation(fields: [technicianProfileId], references: [id])

  @@index([ticketId])
  @@index([technicianProfileId])
  @@index([category])
  @@index([createdAt])
}

